    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>When an endless snowstorm traps a parent and child in a remote cabin, they discover its horrific history.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757060/extras/3af9737ea8ee182733cde9b87f64165a.avif?t=1765225746\" width=590 height=96 /></span><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wintertwined will be a narrative focussed, puzzle horror game.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>You take control of Winter, a shy but snarky young adult, who’s trying to get back “home” safely.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With the aid of Giles, Winter's parental guardian, the two of them must work together to survive the snowy apocalypse.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757060/extras/4f7e48074dd2436c6a64bb361769612b.avif?t=1765225746\" width=590 height=96 /></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wintertwined is currently in development and planned for a commercial release somewhere in the future.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• A slow burn mystery with multiple endings  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Original soundtrack by Harumi Makoto </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Puzzles with 3 difficulty levels  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Original spritework</p>",
